{
  "video_id": "N5NwgUg6eYQ",
  "title": "A digital camera without display - Exploring Porto with the Leica M-D",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 8119.0,
      "end_time": 10239.0,
      "text": "The moment I took my first photo"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 10360.0,
      "end_time": 12799.0,
      "text": "I knew this is what I want to do for the rest of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14760.0,
      "end_time": 19120.0,
      "text": "I think the main worry we must have when we photograph"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20800.0,
      "end_time": 22920.0,
      "text": "is to obtain the best images possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23400.0,
      "end_time": 26000.0,
      "text": "in the right moment, in the moment of the click."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28160.0,
      "end_time": 32000.0,
      "text": "Taking pictures of strangers on the street in a way that it&#39;s obvious"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32119.0,
      "end_time": 33760.0,
      "text": "is a nerve-wrecking, scary job."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 44320.0,
      "end_time": 48760.0,
      "text": "Portugal is really different from where I have been to around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 48840.0,
      "end_time": 51160.0,
      "text": "and everything here inspires me."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 52280.0,
      "end_time": 55240.0,
      "text": "My photos change from \"this my lifestyle\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 55320.0,
      "end_time": 58600.0,
      "text": "to travelling and seeing the world through my eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 65480.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67440.0,
      "text": "Being able to travel opened up many doors."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 67520.0,
      "end_time": 70920.0,
      "text": "I see many things, and it has changed my perspective of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 71920.0,
      "end_time": 74480.0,
      "text": "So I wanted to share that with my friends and family"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 74560.0,
      "end_time": 78800.0,
      "text": "because there are a lot of people that have never seen stuff like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 83480.0,
      "end_time": 88880.0,
      "text": "My philosophy of photographing is to just capture what you like."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 89320.0,
      "end_time": 92240.0,
      "text": "At the end of the day all the photos are for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 93480.0,
      "end_time": 98120.0,
      "text": "If you just try to impress people you lose sight of photography."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 98920.0,
      "end_time": 103400.0,
      "text": "You should only take photos for yourself because that&#39;s what you like to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 103120.0,
      "end_time": 104560.0,
      "text": "This impresses people."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 104640.0,
      "end_time": 107400.0,
      "text": "Always think back to why you have started photography,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 108520.0,
      "end_time": 109800.0,
      "text": "why you appreciate it"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 109880.0,
      "end_time": 112199.0,
      "text": "and be yourself instead of someone else."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 113800.0,
      "end_time": 115759.0,
      "text": "It pushes me to continue doing things like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 116920.0,
      "end_time": 120560.0,
      "text": "Not just for people to travel but also to inspire people to do what they love."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 147560.0,
      "end_time": 150600.0,
      "text": "Part of the experience is that in my head"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 150720.0,
      "end_time": 155280.0,
      "text": "there is this running monologue of justifying myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 155680.0,
      "end_time": 159400.0,
      "text": "So I spend the whole day rationalizing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 159640.0,
      "end_time": 161399.0,
      "text": "explaining myself to myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 161760.0,
      "end_time": 163239.0,
      "text": "Especially because I&#39;m doing something"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 163320.0,
      "end_time": 167920.0,
      "text": "that, a lot of the time, makes people temporarily uncomfortable"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 168520.0,
      "end_time": 169680.0,
      "text": "which is not my nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 171920.0,
      "end_time": 174760.0,
      "text": "In a conscious way there are a lot of questions like"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 175360.0,
      "end_time": 181840.0,
      "text": "how do I walk through the world as a gigantic, hairy two-year-old."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 182800.0,
      "end_time": 185800.0,
      "text": "I think this is why my instinct is to put the camera low"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 186680.0,
      "end_time": 191400.0,
      "text": "because the world is unbelievable from waist height."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 201880.0,
      "end_time": 206720.0,
      "text": "So the excitement isn&#39;t about a wild photo."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 208000.0,
      "end_time": 210840.0,
      "text": "The excitement is an addiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 210960.0,
      "end_time": 213520.0,
      "text": "When it works right it feels like you have superpowers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 214360.0,
      "end_time": 218160.0,
      "text": "that you could distil this crazy unexpected thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 218240.0,
      "end_time": 220120.0,
      "text": "from the whole mess of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 233360.0,
      "end_time": 238680.0,
      "text": "There is this very instinctual attraction to photography"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 238760.0,
      "end_time": 241640.0,
      "text": "because our existence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 242400.0,
      "end_time": 244240.0,
      "text": "no matter how full it gets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 244760.0,
      "end_time": 248760.0,
      "text": "is lonely, and short, and meaningless."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 251680.0,
      "end_time": 256800.0,
      "text": "Being able to present your experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 256920.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259400.00000000003,
      "text": "as something concrete,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 259480.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263680.0,
      "text": "is like &#39;this is my story as I saw it, this is my life as I tell it.&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 265200.0,
      "end_time": 268159.0,
      "text": "Witness me, validate my existence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 268760.0,
      "end_time": 274159.0,
      "text": "let me be more than this fleck of dust in the air."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 287680.0,
      "end_time": 289840.0,
      "text": "I photograph because I love people."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 290600.0,
      "end_time": 292400.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the only way I photograph."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 292480.0,
      "end_time": 295800.0,
      "text": "If the people didn&#39;t exist in the streets"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 295480.0,
      "end_time": 298400.0,
      "text": "neither would my photographs."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 304760.0,
      "end_time": 307599.0,
      "text": "I think it is very important to like people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 307720.0,
      "end_time": 311200.0,
      "text": "to understand, to respect, to listen to people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 311880.0,
      "end_time": 316840.0,
      "text": "and to establish a kind of chemical relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 316960.0,
      "end_time": 322440.0,
      "text": "between the photographer and the subject of the photography."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 322680.0,
      "end_time": 325560.0,
      "text": "In my case it&#39;s people."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 334800.0,
      "end_time": 339440.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the reason I want to give the photos I made"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 339520.0,
      "end_time": 341440.0,
      "text": "to the people in the streets."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 342280.0,
      "end_time": 344919.0,
      "text": "Sometimes, I come back later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 345480.0,
      "end_time": 349840.0,
      "text": "and always give the photos to the people I photographed in the streets."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 353880.0,
      "end_time": 358000.0,
      "text": "I think this is very human and good"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 358120.0,
      "end_time": 361400.0,
      "text": "because they feel important, and they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 364280.0,
      "end_time": 368000.0,
      "text": "You transmit what you know, and what you&#39;ve learned with the others."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 368800.0,
      "end_time": 371480.0,
      "text": "You only transmit when you take a photograph"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 371600.0,
      "end_time": 372800.0,
      "text": "and show it."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 379120.0,
      "end_time": 381920.0,
      "text": "What you are showing is a bit of yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 382800.0,
      "end_time": 386200.0,
      "text": "This is our way to transmit our feelings."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 387440.0,
      "end_time": 391400.0,
      "text": "Not only the feelings of the subject that is photographed"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 392400.0,
      "end_time": 394320.0,
      "text": "but also the feelings of the photographer."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 399120.0,
      "end_time": 402520.0,
      "text": "However, the discipline that you have to have with film"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 402640.0,
      "end_time": 405960.0,
      "text": "is lost with digital photography."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 407480.0,
      "end_time": 410520.0,
      "text": "I was shooting all the different kinds of cameras."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 410640.0,
      "end_time": 414400.0,
      "text": "It was pretty much: point, shoot, burst... Whatever."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 414120.0,
      "end_time": 416800.0,
      "text": "It became really boring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 416160.0,
      "end_time": 418120.0,
      "text": "and my interest in photography started to die"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 418240.0,
      "end_time": 419840.0,
      "text": "until I switched over to Leica."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 420520.0,
      "end_time": 423479.0,
      "text": "Everything felt genuine with Leica."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 424760.0,
      "end_time": 430159.0,
      "text": "In a moment where technology is all about adding features"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 430280.0,
      "end_time": 434159.0,
      "text": "I think that uncomplicating a beautiful camera"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 435000.0,
      "end_time": 438920.0,
      "text": "does the photographer the great favor"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 439400.0,
      "end_time": 441520.0,
      "text": "of letting them not think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 446640.0,
      "end_time": 448880.0,
      "text": "When I&#39;m shooting with this camera"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 448960.0,
      "end_time": 451000.0,
      "text": "I always look at the back on the screen"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 451800.0,
      "end_time": 452600.0,
      "text": "if there&#39;s going to be a picture there."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 452720.0,
      "end_time": 454240.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s no screen."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 454320.0,
      "end_time": 457640.0,
      "text": "All you have is a little knob where you scroll for your ISO."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 457720.0,
      "end_time": 462400.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a visceral thrill when you&#39;re taking these photos."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 462520.0,
      "end_time": 464359.0,
      "text": "Because just like film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 464480.0,
      "end_time": 466720.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t know what you&#39;ve got until later on."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 471240.0,
      "end_time": 475880.0,
      "text": "With this camera we came back to the discipline of film."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 476240.0,
      "end_time": 481000.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s kind of the perfect tool for this little dream bubble"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 481800.0,
      "end_time": 483000.0,
      "text": "of a long weekend."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 487400.0,
      "end_time": 489719.0,
      "text": "We are an unlikely trio."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 489840.0,
      "end_time": 494679.0,
      "text": "We cover a very wide range of perspective and personality."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 496840.0,
      "end_time": 501679.0,
      "text": "It has been a brilliant chemical reaction: mixing us together."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 503800.0,
      "end_time": 506320.0,
      "text": "They are so different photographers."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 506400.0,
      "end_time": 508640.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m so glad because I know"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 508720.0,
      "end_time": 511360.0,
      "text": "they did a great job here in Porto."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 511760.0,
      "end_time": 514240.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a little proud of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 517159.0,
      "end_time": 519520.0,
      "text": "I learned a lot being around these two."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 519600.0,
      "end_time": 521360.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re fun, they&#39;re funny."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 523520.0,
      "end_time": 525560.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m happy to be able to meet them."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 530600.0,
      "end_time": 534400.0,
      "text": "I think the philosophy is to live life"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 534160.0,
      "end_time": 536719.0,
      "text": "with your eyes as wide open as you can get them."
    }
  ]
}